transcription.text:
Speaker 1: This is John, how can I help you?

Speaker 2: Yes sir, I need to order a few bottles of Vasanite.

Speaker 1: Okay, give me one second please.

Speaker 2: Is this Robert Flores?

Speaker 1: Yes.

Speaker 2: Okay.

Speaker 1: How many were you looking to get today, sir?

Speaker 2: I wanted to get the buy two and get two free.

Speaker 1: Okay.

Speaker 2: I'll give that to you today, but you're late on that deal, sir.

Speaker 1: That was for last week, one second.

Speaker 2: Is it still East Valley Drive?

Speaker 1: Yes sir.

Speaker 2: Okay.

Speaker 1: So with shipping and handling it's going to be $109.85, sir.

Speaker 2: You're going to get four total bottles.

Speaker 1: Would you like me to use the Visa then to 9445?

Speaker 2: Yes sir.

Speaker 1: Okay.

Speaker 2: That card declined, sir.

Speaker 1: The 44...

Speaker 2: 9445.

Speaker 1: It declined?

Speaker 2: Yeah, well, I paid for it, it's paid.

Speaker 1: I'm not late on the payment, I can't see why it declined.

Speaker 2: Yeah, your bank could be doing it, so you need to call them, sir, because we didn't decline it.

Speaker 1: It was on the bank.

Speaker 2: All right, let's try another one then.

Speaker 1: Okay.

Speaker 2: Ready when you are.

Speaker 1: Okay.

Speaker 2: 41, 47, 76, 85, 76, 78, 85, 640.

Speaker 1: Expiration?

Speaker 2: 11-26.

Speaker 1: And then the code on the back.

Speaker 2: 7-10.

Speaker 1: Pardon me, it cut out.

Speaker 2: 7-1-0.

Speaker 1: Thank you.

Speaker 2: Okay, that one went through.

Speaker 1: We're all set, you're going to get four bottles sent out to you, sir.

Speaker 2: All right, will it take like three days?

Speaker 1: It'll ship within one to two days, so you should have it in about a week.

Speaker 2: All right, appreciate it.

Speaker 1: Thanks.

Speaker 2: Bye-bye.
